  ('en', 'dad', 'Why did the burger sit down? It was tired of being on a roll.', 4),
  ('en', 'food', 'The secret sauce is secret because even the fries keep asking too many questions.', 5),
  ('en', 'burger', 'Aloo Anarkali has main character energy. One bite and your plain lunch starts feeling underdressed.', 6),
  ('en', 'desi', 'This is the kind of food that makes your inner uncle say, beta, order one more for the table.', 7),
