  ('en', 'food', 'Seasoned Fries: because plain potatoes had dreams too.', 16),
  ('en', 'burger', 'Paneer burgers walk in soft, leave with full desi street confidence.', 17),
  ('en', 'dad', 'What did the patty say to the bun? I am falling for you, layer by layer.', 18),
